### Families — Create, read, update family and prize rules

### Create a family
POST {{host}}/api/families
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Smith Family",
  "weekStartDay": 1
}

###

### Get my family
GET {{host}}/api/families/mine
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update family settings
PATCH {{host}}/api/families/mine
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Smith Family",
  "weekStartDay": 1
}

###

### Update prize eligibility rules (admin only)
PATCH {{host}}/api/families/mine/prize-rules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "weeklyMinDeeds": 5,
  "monthlyMinDeeds": 20
}
